We fitted a Generalised Additive Mixed Model (GAMM) to examine which traits influenced viral sharing among mammal pairs using accelerated discretized implementation in the mgcv package45. We fitted viral sharing (0/1) as the response variable, with a binomial family specification. The model had the following structure:\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
